metadata.name: Queen Honey
metadata.description: Welcome to Berkley Rose Studio. Gritty Graffiti- It’s how our artist expresses his ideas.  Each NFT is an original physical art piece that we have digitalized for a larger community to appreciate.  Our unique selection tells a story and represents an important attribute and virtue in life. This collection represents Tenacity.  It’s a powerful word that plays an important role in all of our lives. Tenacity is the courage to find your way, even through the most challenging times. We hope that our art work will create some inspiring ideas, significant insights or simply bring a smile to your face. Enjoy collecting our unusual paintings or gather several that speak to your heart.
